&lt;p&gt;The post holder will supervise the running of the diagnostics units, liaising with medical staff, patients, GPs, external bodies, outpatient and day ward staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work effectively within a multidisciplinary team to ensure continuity of one of the following services: cross cover will be required to cover sickness and Annual leave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cardiac diagnostic investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respiratory diagnostic investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Neurophysiology diagnostic investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for coordinating and booking all clinics working closely with the multidisciplinary.&lt;/p&gt;
